  "description": "This individual is an undead figure whose skinTone is zombie, stretched tight over prominent bone ridges and a jaw set slightly askew from long decay. Gray eyes sit deep in darkened sockets, and brown hair persists in sparse, brittle clumps across a scalp scarred by old fissure-stone abrasions. The frame is lean to the point of gauntness, with elongated fingers and hardened joints that preserve the stiff economy of movement typical of reanimated remains. Their presence is marked by the disciplined stillness of something bound to a site of death, maintaining a tireless vigilance amid ruin rather than any living rhythm.",
